### POST example
POST {{url}}/poem/
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "title": "Sunrise paints the sky",
  "poem": "Sunrise paints the sky, Gentle waves kiss sandy shores, Day awakens slow.",
  "style": "Haiku"
}

